7.3 무더위 쉼터 주말 운영, 야간 연장 운영, 숙박 가능 비율¶

In [51]:
close_night = len(df_shelter.loc[df_shelter[""]==is_open_nights[0]])
open_night = len(df_shelter.loc[df_shelter[""]==is_open_nights[1]])
no_info_night = len(df_shelter.loc[df_shelter[""].isna()])
open_night_info = np.array([close_night, open_night, no_info_night])

close_night_close_weekend = len(df_shelter.loc[(df_shelter[""]==is_open_nights[0]) & (df_shelter[""]==is_open_weekends[0])])
close_night_open_weekend = len(df_shelter.loc[(df_shelter[""]==is_open_nights[0]) & (df_shelter[""]==is_open_weekends[1])])
close_night_no_info_weekend = len(df_shelter.loc[(df_shelter[""]==is_open_nights[0]) & (df_shelter[""].isna())])
open_night_close_weekend = len(df_shelter.loc[(df_shelter[""]==is_open_nights[1]) & (df_shelter[""]==is_open_weekends[0])])
open_night_open_weekend = len(df_shelter.loc[(df_shelter[""]==is_open_nights[1]) & (df_shelter[""]==is_open_weekends[1])])
